Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.51,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an9}You're My Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.92,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an9}ココロを開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:07.77,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an9}打ち明けたいゆずれない想いを
